  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, combine lamb, onion, garlic, paprika, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper. Mix well.",
    "3. Add the tripe to the bowl and mix until coated with the spice mixture.",
    "4. Thread the lamb and tripe mixture onto skewers.",
    "5. Brush the olive oil onto the skewers.",
    "6. Grill the kebabs for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, until the lamb is cooked through and the tripe is tender.",
    "7. Serve hot, garnished with parsley."
